16
00:00:41,842 --> 00:00:44,811 line:-2
I think at the root
of that meltdown


17
00:00:44.845 --> 00:00:47.481 line:-1 align:center
was something that everybody


18
00:00:47,514 --> 00:00:52,986 line:-2
who is part of this conference
