19
00:00:53,020 --> 00:00:56,390 line:-2
I arrived at "ABC News"
at the big leagues,


20
00:00:56.423 --> 00:01:00.260 line:-2 align:center
the network, at the tender age
of 28 years old,


21
00:01:00,294 --> 00:01:04,731 line:-2
and I was really anxious
about being so young


22
00:01:04.765 --> 00:01:08.035 line:-2 align:center
and being so inexperienced,
