23
00:01:08,068 --> 00:01:13,273 line:-2
into my work in a really, really
sort of workaholic-style way.


24
00:01:13,307 --> 00:01:15,776 line:-2
And shortly after
I arrived at "ABC News,"


25
00:01:15.809 --> 00:01:19.112 line:-2 align:center
