30
00:01:30,390 --> 00:01:32,593 line:-1
Gaza, a lot of time in Iraq…


31
00:01:32.626 --> 00:01:36.997 line:-1 align:center
six or seven long stays in Iraq.


32
00:01:37.030 --> 00:01:38.866 line:-2 align:center
And I came home
