a sleeve of Oreos,


119
00:05:13.013 --> 00:05:15.949 line:-2 align:center
but I would notice the urge
and, instead of acting on it


120
00:05:15,983 --> 00:05:19,887 line:-2
reflexively, I would be able
to respond wisely.


121
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,856 line:-2
And that was really--
it doesn't work all the time,


122
00:05:22,890 --> 00:05:25,325 line:-2
which is why I call my book
"Ten Percent Happier,"


123
00:05:25,359 --> 00:05:27,294 line:-2
but when it does work,
it's a game changer,


124
00:05:27,327 --> 00:05:31,498 line:-2
and it is a skill that you
can improve over time.


125
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:34,468 line:-2
So as advertised
