189
00:08:37,017 --> 00:08:39,253 line:-1
to taking care of yourself


190
00:08:39.286 --> 00:08:41.455 line:-2 align:center
so that you can be
maximally effective,


191
00:08:41,488 --> 00:08:44,691 line:-2
and I think there are
probably at least five


192
00:08:44,725 --> 00:08:46,660 line:-2
other things I would
put in this pantheon.


193
00:08:46,693 --> 00:08:48,228 line:-1
So start with meditation,


194
00:08:48.262 --> 00:08:52.032 line:-2 align:center
but I would also add sleep,
