207
00:09:24,998 --> 00:09:28,669 line:-2
The quality
of your relationships--


208
00:09:28.702 --> 00:09:30.871 line:-2 align:center
now I'm stealing a quote
from somebody else,


209
00:09:30,904 --> 00:09:33,974 line:-2
so I'll own that
