554
00:25:43.544 --> 00:25:46.079 line:-2 align:center
off the cushion
in your actual life,


555
00:25:46.113 --> 00:25:48.115 line:-2 align:center
you're less likely
to be owned by it.


556
00:25:48,148 --> 00:25:50,384 line:-2
That's what we're doing here
in meditation is getting


557
00:25:50.417 --> 00:25:53.520 line:-2 align:center
more familiar with the workings
of our own mind


558
00:25:53.554 --> 00:25:56.190 line:-2 align:center
so that it's not yanking us
around all the time,


559
00:25:56.223 --> 00:25:58.759 line:-2 align:center
so that we can learn
how to respond wisely


560
00:25:58,792 --> 00:26:02,829 line:-2
to the things in our life
instead of reacting blindly.


561
00:26:02,863 --> 00:26:04,765 line:-2
So anyway, Jeff,
I just said a bunch of stuff.


